# GuiaSat — environment template. Copy to `.env` (which is git-ignored) and
# fill in locally. NEVER commit a real key.
#
# AI tutor (the persistent chat assistant). The key is read by the BACKEND
# only (server/), never bundled into the browser, so it can't leak via the
# shipped frontend. With no key set, the tutor runs fully offline on its
# seeded answer library — no network calls, no cost.
#
# The same key powers the live mission CONSULTANT (POST /consult in
# server/flash.js, model claude-opus-4-8). With no key set, the consultant
# runs on its offline heuristic engine — the digital twin still drives the
# draft component list and warnings; only the prose advice is local.
#
# Note: no VITE_ prefix on purpose — VITE_-prefixed vars are exposed in the
# client bundle; this one must stay server-side.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
